# Repository notes (displayed after build)
NOTES="Press INSERT to en/disable the MAME's system settings key while a system is running. Then use TAB to activate the system settings menu.

MAME configuration files are usually stored in /home/<user name>/.mame/. Look for ___empty.ini or mame.ini and look for ui.ini.
It is quicker to edit MAME software/game location URIs in the ini files than to do it in the MAME UI.

Put your category index files (e.g. catlist.ini, catver.ini, genre.ini, genre_ows.ini, mature.ini and not_mature.ini) in /home/<user name>/.mame/UI/.
These can be download from https://www.progettosnaps.net/catver/. They are zipped files. Put the unzipped files in in /home/<user name>/.mame/UI/.
Remember to check/update the correct mame.ini or ___empty.ini with the correct location of your category files; or press TAB in the MAME UI and set their loaction in general settings.

After configuring the locations of your ini, software and dat files, remember to hit the magnifying glass icon in the MAME UI; this tells MAME to audit your media/files."
